headline.print_headline: Teheran, Zimmermann Each Throw 3 Scoreless Innings
headline.main: Teheran, Zimmermann Each Throw 3 Scoreless Innings

lead_paragraph: Julio Teheran worked around six base runners to match Jordan Zimmermann with three scoreless innings and lead the Atlanta Braves to a 3-2 win over the Atlanta Braves on Thursday night.
